Build a Shiny app using the following datasets (in datasets library):

mtcars
USArrests
uspop

Publish the App to https://www.shinyapps.io account
Build a Shiny app loaded with your own data sets
Insert an iframe to your GitHub website/page to showcase your data and charts

Example:
&lt;iframe width="800" height="600"
src="https://karlho.shinyapps.io/AnimationShiny/?_ga=
